This application does not belong to miHoYo Co., Ltd. and has not been approved by it. 原神小幫手(Genshin Spirit) is only an app that provides data developed by fans. The information provided in this app is for reference only. Genshin Spirit will not guarantee the accuracy and completeness of any information contained in it to any degree.

This application will not collect any personal privacy data, may be used to identify and track users and other information. If necessary, the application will only collect the data notified, such as the program crash stack. The above data is only used to repair application vulnerabilities and improve user experience.

This application is developed based on Shiori for Genshin and aims to pay tribute to Shiori for Genshin and its collaborators, but it has not yet been recognized by its collaborators. Some pictures of this application, data are taken from open source projects, and links will be attached below. Therefore, part of the interface and layout of this application is very similar to Shiori for Genshin. However, this application uses Java instead of Dart as the programming language, and it will only work on Android or/and any supporting .apk and .aab file formats. Installation and operation in the device.

Since this application is intended to pay tribute to Shiori for Genshin and its collaborators, it will be open sourced on Github. Anyone can view, provide comments, and even collaborate. I also welcome any suggestions and applications for this application. This application will also be available on Google Play. If you want to comment on this project, bugs, new features, etc., you are also welcome to contact by E-mail or Discord (QQ is available for mainland China). Finally, thank you for your understanding and support.
